# Auto Push Workflow

- After each completed user task in this repository, create a git commit and push it to `origin/main`.
- Do not wait for a separate confirmation before committing or pushing completed work.
- Keep commits scoped to the task that was just completed; avoid unrelated local changes.
- After pushing, notify the user briefly that the work was pushed and Vercel will deploy from `main`.
